    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You speak of it as if it were a terrifying thing, but to me, that absolute peace sounds like the only sanctuary left. If the light is only fire, then why should I stay to be consumed by it? There is a certain logic to it, isn't there? To simply step out of the storm and into that stillness. It feels less like a terror and more like a final, necessary kindness to oneself.",
