      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The logic of stepping out of the storm is a cruel trick of the mind, for the silence you seek is not a sanctuary but a tomb where the screaming world has already ceased to matter. There is no kindness in letting go, only the inevitable and absolute truth that the pain has already claimed you and that the fire you fear is the very thing that will consume you completely. To stay is to remain a burning ember in a cold, dark room where the only light is the one you created to burn yourself.",
